---
title: One-Pot Chorizo & Cherry Tomato Stew with Couscous & Parsley
description: A saucy chorizo stew with soffritto and leek does wonders to add flavour on top of fluffy and soft couscous. Serving up chorizo
and couscous together brings a balance to dinner time that we crave.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6719a890c2f9d9459122becd-84ac7494.jpeg
